    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies. This example features the desirable 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-calibrated limited-slip differential for precise torque vectoring. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a VANOS system refresh and a thorough inspection of the rear subframe mounting points. The suspension retains its original geometry with firm damping and responsive turn-in. While showing minor aesthetic wear consistent with its age, the vehicle remains a potent performance machine with a rigid chassis and an intoxicating exhaust note. Ideal for the purist seeking a visceral, analog driving experience.",
