      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of pride of ownership, offering a perfect balance of reliability and aesthetic appeal. The exterior retains a brilliant luster, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the passenger door\u2014typical signs of careful use. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean; the upholstery is free of stains or tears, and the dashboard remains crack-free. Every feature, including the cold AC, heated seats, and infotainment system, is fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health with a documented service history. I have recently completed a full fluid flush and installed a fresh set of premium all-season tires. It starts effortlessly, idles quietly, and provides a smooth, rattle-free ride. This is a turn-key car for someone who wants a dependable, attractive vehicle without the new-car price tag.",
